#!/bin/sh
#$log ist's a name of snort's log file for eg. alert, */* .
log='*/*'
path='/home/services/httpd/html/snort'
wyr='\/home\/services\/httpd\/html\/snort\/'

rm $path/*
cat /var/log/snort/$log | /usr/bin/snortalog.pl -g gif -h $path/index.html
cat $path/index.html |sed -e 's/$wyr//g' > $path/index.html
chmod 644 $path/*
